""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ContactDetailsId], [t].[Name], [t].[Id0], [t].[Email], [t].[PhoneNo], [l].[Id], [l].[City], [l].[Country], [l].[CustomerId], [l].[PostalCode], [l].[Street], [l].[StreetNumber]
